trans-unit.source: Troubleshooting Guides for Azure Mobile Engagement
trans-unit.target: Troubleshooting Guides for Azure Mobile Engagement

trans-unit.source: The following troubleshooting guides cover the most common issues with Azure Mobile Engagement, with the exception of [billing][Link 11] questions and assistance signing up for the [preview][Link 7].
trans-unit.target: The following troubleshooting guides cover the most common issues with Azure Mobile Engagement, with the exception of [billing][Link 11] questions and assistance signing up for the [preview][Link 7].

trans-unit.source: If you aren't able to resolve your issue with these troubleshooting guides you can either open an Azure service request - if you have an [Azure Support Agreement](http://azure.microsoft.com/support/options/) - or you can request assistance on the [MSDN Forum][Link 8].
trans-unit.target: If you aren't able to resolve your issue with these troubleshooting guides you can either open an Azure service request - if you have an [Azure Support Agreement](http://azure.microsoft.com/support/options/) - or you can request assistance on the [MSDN Forum][Link 8].

trans-unit.source: Make sure to include all the troubleshooting information from [Service Request Info](mobile-engagement-troubleshooting-guide-sr-info.md) when you open a service request to help technical support to investigate your issue.
